        <h2>Key Features of Trae AI</h2>
        
        <h3>The "Think-Before-Doing" Approach</h3>
        <p>At the core of Trae AI's innovation is its methodical approach to problem-solving. Rather than immediately generating content or code in response to a prompt, Trae AI first analyzes the request, breaks it down into logical components, and plans its execution strategy before producing any output.</p>
        
        <p>This deliberate process results in higher quality outputs with fewer errors and better alignment with user intentions. The system effectively mimics the thought process of an experienced developer or content creator, considering dependencies, potential issues, and optimal implementation paths.</p>
        
