          <h4>Builder Mode</h4>
          <p>Trae AI's Builder mode exemplifies the think-before-doing philosophy by providing a systematic task breakdown for complex operations. When asked to create a feature or solve a problem, Builder mode will:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Analyze the current project structure</li>
            <li>Break down the task into logical steps</li>
            <li>Outline dependencies and requirements</li>
            <li>Present a clear execution plan</li>
            <li>Implement the solution with careful consideration of the existing codebase</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Dual Chat Interfaces</h3>
        <p>Trae AI offers two complementary chat interfaces that serve different purposes in the development workflow:</p>
        
