              <li>Learning about new concepts or technologies</li>
              <li>Exploring alternative approaches to problems</li>
              <li>Getting guidance on best practices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>Inline Chat</h4>
            <p>The Inline Chat interface is contextually aware and appears directly within your code or content. It excels at:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Providing context-specific suggestions</li>
              <li>Explaining code or content sections</li>
              <li>Making targeted improvements to existing work</li>
              <li>Offering real-time assistance as you create</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>This dual-interface approach allows Trae AI to support both high-level strategic thinking and detailed implementation work, making it a versatile companion throughout the entire development process.</p>
        
        <h3>Multimodal Input Support</h3>
