        <ul>
          <li>Share screenshots of code or design mockups for analysis</li>
          <li>Upload reference images to guide content creation</li>
          <li>Provide visual examples to clarify requirements</li>
          <li>Extract text or data from images for processing</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>The multimodal support significantly enhances communication efficiency, allowing users to express their needs more naturally and comprehensively.</p>
        
