        </ul>
        
        <p>These models provide Trae AI with the intelligence needed to understand complex requests, generate high-quality content, and offer insightful suggestions across various domains.</p>
        
        <h3>Model Context Protocol (MCP) Integration</h3>
        <p>Trae AI integrates with the Model Context Protocol (MCP), enabling it to access external tools and services. This integration extends Trae AI's capabilities beyond its built-in functions, allowing it to:</p>
